snippet.title: AMBER Alert, search continues for 13-year-old whose parents were found dead
snippet.description:
An Amber Alert has been issued for a 13-year-old girl believed to have been taken from the residence where her parents were found dead Monday morning. NCMEC says Jayme Closs was taken from her home Monday morning, likely at gunpoint. https://kare11.tv/2OsYkkO
